newdata <- read.csv(file = '/Users/LJL/Documents/GU 2021 Fall/Anly 501/Data Cleaning/hsi_features_new.csv')
newdata = subset(newdata, select = -c(label, ticker))

predict.kmeans <- function(object, newdata){
    centers <- object$centers
    n_centers <- nrow(centers)
    dist_mat <- as.matrix(dist(rbind(centers, newdata)))
    dist_mat <- dist_mat[-seq(n_centers), seq(n_centers)]
    max.col(-dist_mat)
}
set.seed(27)
mod_kmeans <- kmeans(data, 3)

test_preds <- predict(mod_kmeans, newdata)
set.seed(27)
mod_kmeans <- kmeans(new, 3)
fviz_cluster(mod_kmeans, new, geom = "point")
